Barroso Says to Press G-20 for Global Financial-Transactions Tax

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-05T13:33:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/barroso-says-to-press-g-20-for-global-financial-transactions-tax.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said he will push for a global financial-transactions
tax at the Group of 20 nations.  He spoke at a press conference today in Brussels.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
